data.description: Beautiful 2 Story Home Planted in Trail Ridge Community with a Beautiful Pool, Playground and Cabanas. The property has a Upstairs Loft,  3 Bedrooms, with Mountain views. Fantastic Location Just minutes away from the New Durango Station Hotel Casino and Resort, With Restaurants, Shopping Centers, Blue Diamond, and Freeways near by. This Beautiful Property has Mohawk Wood Flooring through-out downstairs, Customs Cabinets built-ins in the Family room, ,Windom jams and cased, Crown Moldings and Custom Paneling, Ceiling Fans through-out, Separate Laundry room, Granite Kitchen, Stainless Appliances.
